        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 2: Immunostaining using affinity-purified anti-Stau2 antibodies and mAbs specific for the postsynaptic marker protein PSD95 revealed that discrete Stau2 particles were distributed along the dendritic shaft beneath PSD95-positive puncta (in cultured mature hippocampal neurons).. Experimental description: \"Rat hippocampal neurons were cultured\"\n\nantibody source was not specified" ;
